\section{Uncertainty layer}{

When \code{include_uncertainty = TRUE} an additional raster layer is appended
whose values are the \emph{posterior SD of the linear predictor} at each cell,
propagated through all environmental betas. This encodes where the model is
most uncertain about environmental conditions,
